\\beta/(6\\beta-4)}$. In particular, the error is at most of order\n$\\tau^{-1/6}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Jan 2011 07:35:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2011-01-10"}
