ucture\npositions at different frequencies correspond to different components of a\nsource.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 7 Jan 2011 15:59:45 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Jun 2011 11:59:23 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-03-17"}
